00:12:12.333 --> 00:12:14.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Gelecek taşınabilir görünüyor.

149
00:12:14.916 --> 00:12:17.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
