174
00:13:35.250 --> 00:13:39.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Geçidi içindeki
insanlarla birlikte kapatacağız.

175
00:13:40.666 --> 00:13:43.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
