nasıl koruyacağız ki?

177
00:13:47.916 --> 00:13:50.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Braila'da öyle çok asker kaybettik ki,

178
00:13:50.541 --> 00:13:53.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
komşularımız saldırırsa kendimizi

179
00:13:53.250 --> 00:13:54.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
nasıl savunuruz, bilmem.

180
00:13:55.375 --> 00:13:58.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Demir Ustası Hector hücrede.

181
00:13:59.125 --> 00:14:01.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hector gece yaratığı yapabilir.

182
00:14:02.250 --> 00:14:05.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Başka bir işe yaramayan alçak
bize cehennemin sürüsünden

183
00:14:05.875 --> 00:14:08.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
