225
00:16:34.500 --> 00:16:35.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hayır.

226
00:17:18.416 --> 00:17:20.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sanırım artık uyandım.

227
00:17:21.583 --> 00:17:22.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Peki...

228
00:17:22.875 --> 00:17:23.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Pardon?

229
00:17:24.166 --> 00:17:25.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aferin.

230
00:17:43.375 --> 00:17:44.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Çok güzel kokuyor.

231
00:17:45.333 --> 00:17:46.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İki tane alabilir miyim?

232
00:17:47.583 --> 00:17:48.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Benden olsun.

233
00:17:50.625 --> 00:17:51.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bay Belmont.

234
00:17:52.083 --> 00:17:56.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Vay, ne heybetli bir canavarsın sen.

235
00:17:57.083 --> 00:17:58.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İzin verir misin?

236
00:17:58.708 --> 00:17:59.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Buyur.

237
00:17:59.750 --> 00:18:03.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Asil Belmont Hanedanı'nın
amblemini tabii ki tanıyorum,

238
00:18:03.333 --> 00:18:04.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
pelerininin üstündeki.

239
00:18:05.625 --> 00:18:09.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Aslında bu güzel pelerin
daha iyi günler gördü, değil mi?

240
00:18:10.458 --> 00:18:12.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Belki şu yerel ustalardan biri onu

241
00:18:12.958 --> 00:18:14.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
