Kimsin cehennemlik herif?

245
00:18:20.666 --> 00:18:22.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aynen. Cehennem.

246
00:18:22.458 --> 00:18:24.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bu konuda konuşmalıyız.

247
00:18:24.875 --> 00:18:25.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ama önce...

248
00:18:27.291 --> 00:18:29.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
...bırak da sana kendimi tanıtayım.

249
00:18:30.708 --> 00:18:32.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ben Saint Germain Kontuyum.

250
00:18:32.875 --> 00:18:35.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Herhalde ailen sana hakkımdaki
hikayeleri anlatmıştır.

251
00:18:36.625 --> 00:18:40.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ailem bana hikaye anlatmak için fazla ölü.

252
00:18:40.916 --> 00:18:41.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ah, tabii ki.

253
00:18:41.875 --> 00:18:45.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tahliye. Çok üzgünüm. Korkunç bir suç.

254
00:18:47.458 --> 00:18:49.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aileni ve ailenin bu ülkedeki

255
00:18:50.083 --> 00:18:53.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
